  <brief_title>Comparing Two Forms of Head Immobilization for Stereotactic Radiotherapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Trial Comparing Two Forms of Immobilization of the Head for Fractioned Stereotactic Radiotherapy</official_title>
